10. Types of Protection Mode ?

=> 3 types of protection mode. 

👉 Maximum Performance Mode (default) - 

	- Minimum dataloss. 
	- Noaffirm and async parameter use.
	- It is a default protection mode.

👉 Maximum Protection Mode :

	- It will have Highest protection.
	- No data lost. 
	- It can have affirm and Sync parameter.

👉 Maximum Availability Mode :

	- It also can give highest protection.
	- It can have Affirm or Noaffirm and Sync parameter use.

